==Operating system support==
The [[operating system]]s on which the editors can run natively (without [[emulator|emulation]] or compatibility layers), meaning which operating systems have which editors specifically coded for them (not, for example, [[Wings 3D]] for [[Microsoft Windows|Windows]] running on [[Linux]] with [[Wine (software)|Wine]]).
