{{refimprove|date=April 2016}} {{Infobox Museum |name = Gyeonggi Museum of Art |image = |caption = |map_type = |map_caption = |coordinates = {{coord|37.325768|126.813874|display=inline}} |established = |location = 268, Dongsan-ro, [[Danwon-gu]], [[Ansan]], [[South Korea]] |type = Contemporary art |visitors = |owner = |website = {{URL|http://gmoma.kr}} {{ko icon}} }} The '''Gyeonggi Museum of Art''', located in [[Ansan]], [[South Korea]], opened in 2006, endeavors to observe, reflect and foster [[contemporary art]] in a regional and national scale in order to enrich the local community's cultural experience.
