'''''Johnstown Magazine''''' is a monthly magazine describing events and activities in the [[Johnstown, Pennsylvania]] and surrounding area.<ref name="bct"/> The magazine began in April 2005.<ref name="bct">{{cite news|title=Johnstown Magazine|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=2002&dat=20050121&id=DXcyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=SrUFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4655,4598918&hl=tr|accessdate=25 August 2016|work=Beaver County Times|date=21 January 2005}}</ref> The magazine is published by [[Community Newspaper Holdings]] based in [[Birmingham, Alabama]].<ref>{{cite news|title=T-D, Johnstown Magazine named top newspaper, magazine|url=http://www.tribdem.com/news/local_news/t-d-johnstown-magazine-named-top-newspaper-magazine/article_1f07e816-d383-5f4c-8b1b-bacb83719ae2.html|accessdate=3 March 2017|work=Tribune-Democrat|date=11 April 2008}}</ref>
